                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Heureux et fier vainqueur du triple Géryon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Arriva sur nos bords le fils d'Amphytrion ;",
