                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Et le roc en tombant ferme le souterrain.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Mais Hercule le voit : il court, frémit de rage,",
