                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et de ses yeux errants cherche au loin un passage.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "En vain de la caverne il tente d'approcher ;",
